		<li><a href="#SynIntPhiCan">1.3 Synoptic Interpretations of the Philosophical Canon</a></li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li><a href="#FemRevHisPhi">2. Feminist Revisions of the History of Philosophy</a>
