		<li><a href="#WomMedPhi">2.2 Women in Medieval Philosophy</a></li>
		<li><a href="#WomLatEigNinCenPhi">2.3 Women in Late Eighteenth and Nineteenth century Philosophy</a></li>
		<li><a href="#HisQue">2.4 Historiographical Questions</a></li>
	</ul>
	</li>
